- audit-004 (MED): PipelineService.WriteInpAsync stdout never drained → potential pipe deadlock.
  Drain stdout+stderr concurrently (mirror MeshingService).
- audit-005 (MED): no CI. Add GitHub Actions (dotnet build/test + pytest + ruff + regression job).
- audit-006 (MED): dependency drift / no lockfile (numpy 1.26.4 pin vs 2.2.6 installed; gmsh,
