- audit-007 (LOW): FEAModel.validate rejects ν=0 and auxetic; allow −1<ν<0.5.
- audit-008 (LOW): FRD float regex assumes 3-digit Windows exponent; relax to {2,3} + fixture.
- audit-009 (LOW): no ruff/mypy/.editorconfig/analyzers.
- audit-010 (LOW): doc drift (148 vs 164 test count; architecture.md bare pointer).
